939
00:53:35,559 --> 00:53:37,039
To survive

940
00:53:37,599 --> 00:53:38,559
is the top priority

941
00:53:38,559 --> 00:53:39,480
to Xiao En at the moment.

942
00:53:39,760 --> 00:53:40,159
Yes!

